You place the emblem firmly in the hole and hear a "click". The tree on the emblem suddenly lights up. It hurts your eyes. A high pitched sound enters your ears and you slowly lose consciousness.

Forest
The sound of police sirens enters your ears. You open your eyes and slowly stand up. Trees surround you. It seems you woke up in a forest. A policeman shouts: "Police! Put your hands up!" You put your hands in the air. "You're arrested for the murder of your wife."
